OL,3,CPubs close early amid 'unrest' as
OL,4,COxford Union prepares for Tommy
OL,5,CRobinson visit
OL,7,FPubs and shops in Oxford city centre
OL,8,Fhave put boards up and confirmed they
OL,9,Fare closing early as the Oxford Union
OL,10,Fprepares to host far-right activist
OL,11,FTommy Robinson.
OL,13,FThe controversial speaker is due to
OL,14,Fattend a debate on Islam on Wednesday
OL,15,Fevening, despite outcry from faith
OL,16,Fleaders, local politicians and
OL,17,Fcampaign groups.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
