OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781770693
OL,3,CPubs close early amid 'unrest' as
OL,4,COxford Union prepares for Tommy
OL,5,CRobinson visit
OL,7,FThe student debate society has
OL,8,Fadvertised a debate on social media
OL,9,Ftitled The West Is Right To Be
OL,10,FSuspicious Of Islam to take place on
OL,11,FJune 17.
OL,13,FBut some pubs are stores have "shut up
OL,14,Fshop" amid warnings of unrest caused
OL,15,Fby Robinson's visit.
OL,17,FProtesters are expected to gather at
OL,18,Fthe Union ahead of the debate,
OL,19,Fsparking fears that it could lead to
OL,20,Fdisorder in the city.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
