OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781770693
OL,3,CPubs close early amid 'unrest' as
OL,4,COxford Union prepares for Tommy
OL,5,CRobinson visit
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, Edward
OL,8,FWhinney, Manager of the White Rabbit
OL,9,Fin Friars Entry has made the decision
OL,10,Fto close early at 4pm.
OL,12,F"For us, it has really been a judgment
OL,13,Fcall on how we keep all of our staff
OL,14,Fand our customers safe," he said.
OL,16,F"The debate this evening seems to be a
OL,17,Fvery sensationalist one.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781770693
OL,3,CPubs close early amid 'unrest' as
OL,4,COxford Union prepares for Tommy
OL,5,CRobinson visit
OL,7,F"It seems to be inflaming lots of
OL,8,Fopinion, and we are expecting there to
OL,9,Fbe protests, and we've had warnings
OL,10,Ffrom both the police and the city
OL,11,Fcentre here in Oxford.
OL,13,F"So as a business, our first priority
OL,14,Fis to look after our staff and our
OL,15,Fcustomers, and if there is a risk,
OL,16,Fwe're not prepared to take that.
OL,18,F"Their safety has to come first."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781770693
OL,3,CPubs close early amid 'unrest' as
OL,4,COxford Union prepares for Tommy
OL,5,CRobinson visit
OL,7,FBen Vernede, Supervisor at The Bear
OL,8,FInn on Alfred Street said they have
OL,9,Fbeen advised by police, that they
OL,10,Fshould not serve alcohol outside.
OL,12,FBut they can remain open for England's
OL,13,Ffirst official World Cup match against
OL,14,FCroatia, as long as they have security
OL,15,Fmeasures in place.
OL,17,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, he said:
OL,18,F"Its put us in a hard position where
OL,19,Fwe were fully booked tonight.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781770693
OL,3,CPubs close early amid 'unrest' as
OL,4,COxford Union prepares for Tommy
OL,5,CRobinson visit
OL,7,F"We've had to cancel all the bookings
OL,8,Ffor the England game due to not being
OL,9,Fable to serve alcohol outside."
OL,11,FSpeakers at the event include
OL,12,FRobinson, whose real name is Stephen
OL,13,FYaxley-Lennon, alongside fellow far-
OL,14,Fright voice Laurence Fox, opposed by
OL,15,Fothers including former Tory MP Jacob
OL,16,FRees-Mogg.
OL,18,FIt was reported last month that the
OL,19,Fdebate had been delayed after
OL,20,Fsignificant outcry about Yaxley-
OL,21,FLennon's attendance.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
